description.en: Galaxy Pool is a blockchain storage project benchmarking the future trillion-level distributed storage market. Galaxy Pool is committed to building a strong, stable, efficient, and high-yield storage mining pool distributed in Asia and even the world. GPO is equity token of Galaxy Pool, and GPO is a new type of on-chain asset that uses smart contracts for the first digital asset issuance. In general terms, participants use GPO assets as mining machines to mine a variety of other digital assets, and gain value-added returns from GPOs through the repurchase and destruction of mining pool profits, allowing users who hold GPOs to obtain higher returns.
